metadata.name: MEMOIR I
metadata.description:
Jubilant exuberance, the air is alive,  
A New Year, new chapter, Ethereum set to thrive  
Nurture the projects’ seeds, NFtokens grow grand  
Unveil those DeFi dreams, like grains of sand  
Aave and Chainlink break through, a robust display  
Raving about ETH 2.0 beacon - pump won’t delay  
Y’all stand braced for more fun? Good, Bull has just begun…
